data.description: $10,000 seller credit available & an assumable interest rate at 2.65%. Tastefully situated on a sprawling lot backed by a greenbelt, this pristine home presents an open-concept floor plan. Constructed by DR Horton, the chef’s kitchen adjoins the living room & breakfast nook, complete with stainless steel appliances and granite counter tops. Retreat to your primary suite with sitting area, large tile shower, dual granite vanity and walk-in closet. Upstairs, enjoy your spacious game room large enough to accommodate an at home office and easy entertaining, 3 bedrooms with walk-in closets & a hall bath. Additional features include an energy efficient design, video doorbell, programmable thermostat and smart lights at the front entry. The neighborhood amenities like walking trails, swimming pool & playgrounds are easily accessed for your enjoyment. This new subdivision is conveniently located just minutes to Lake Bryan, RELLIS Campus & Historic Downtown Bryan.
